high_descs: Turn around and go to the stove.
Pick up the pan on the left side of the stove.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator.
Put the pan inside the refrigerator.
Go to the stand with the coffee maker directly to the left of the refrigerator.
Pick up the knife from the stand.
Cut the tomato on the stand into slices.
Put the knife on the stand.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Go to the right to the refrigerator.
Put the slice of tomato into the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of tomato into the refrigerator with a pan.

high_descs: Turn around to face the stove.
Pick up the pan on the left side of the stove.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and put the pan inside.
Close the refrigerator, turn to the left, walk forward and face the table with the coffee maker on top of it.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Slice the tomato into pieces with the knife.
Put the knife on the table
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn around, walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door and put the tomato inside.
anns.task_desc: Put the pan into the refrigerator, slice up a tomato, put the tomato slice into the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the stove behind you.
Pick up the fry pan on the back, left burner of the stove.
Turn around and go back to the refrigerator.
Place the fry pan on the top shelf of the refrigerator.
Go to the dishwasher to your immediate left.
Pick up the knife between the salt and the tomato, on the dishwasher.
Cut the tomato on the dishwasher into slices.
Place the knife back on the dishwasher, between the fork and the tomato.
Pick up one of the tomato slices, on the dishwasher, previously cut.
Turn to your right, and go back to the refrigerator.
Place the tomato slice in the black pan, on the top shelf of the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a tomato slice in a pan, in the fridge.

high_descs: turn around to face the stove
pick up the griddle pan that is on the back left burner of the stove
turn around and move towards the fridge
open the fridge door, put the pan on the top shelf and close the door
move to the counter to the left of the fridge where the coffee pot is sitting
pick up the sharp knife with the yellow handle from the counter
slice the tomato that is on the counter
put the knife on the counter in front of the coffee machine
pick up a slice of tomato
turn to the right and move forward and turn to face the refrigerator
put the tomato onto the pan that is on the top shelf of the fridge
anns.task_desc: put a slice of tomato on to a chilled pan in the refrigerator

high_descs: Turn around and face the stove.
Pick up the square pan from the back, right part of the stove.
Turn back around and open the fridge.
Place the square pan on the top shelf.
Hold on to the fridge door and close it.
Move to the left to the counter right next to the fridge.
Pick up the large knife that is on the front of the counter.
Slice the tomato that is on the counter.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn Right and go to the fridge.  Open the door.
Place the tomato on the square pan in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: The robot should be able to slice and place a slice of tomato on a square pan in the fridge.

Pick up the pan on the far left of the stove
Turn to your right head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in the pan take it out then close the fridge
Turn to your left then move light turn right to the island
Pick up the knife on the island
Slice the tomato on top of the island
Put the knife on top of the island beside the coffee maker
pick up the the slice tomato
Turn to your right move forward then turn left on the fridge
Open the fridge put in the slice tomato
anns.task_desc: Put the slice tomato in the fridge
